schema.exitNote: This is an exit note written by Sebastián (a-acute accent) and Barnes, which includes a pleasant façade (c-cedilla) and this cast of additional characters: Δ : Greek capital letter Delta (U+0394) Ж : Cyrillic capital letter Zhe with breve (U+04C1) Ŵ : Latin capital letter W with circumflex (U+0174) Ω : Greek capital letter Omega (U+03A9) 月 : Han (CJK) character 'moon; month' ((U+6708)
